ither live on mainnet or in various stages of testnets. If they hit their t=
imelines, Zero Knowledge Proofs could be one of the breakout technologies o=
f 2023.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Today, we&#8217;re going to go deep on one=
 of the most promising companies in the zero-knowledge space: </span><stron=
g><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/bdaa4a75-3cd6-4200-882a-d509d4e1=
