rt for Zero-Knowledge Succinct Non-Interactive Argument of Knowledge), a sp=
ecific type of ZKP. This is how Vitalik introduced ZK-SNARKs:&#160;</span><=
/p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #67bdfc; margin: 20px 0;"><p=
