0px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><span>ZK-SNARKs are a powerful technology. <=
/span><strong><span>ZK-SNARKs may be to cryptography what </span><a href=3D=
"https://substack.com/redirect/849eed8c-a277-485f-aead-6ddbac60ce46?j=3DeyJ=
1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel=3D"" style=
=3D"color: #404040; text-decoration: underline;">transformers</a><span> are=
 to AI</span></strong><span>: a general-purpose technology that is so power=
ful that it will completely steamroll a whole bunch of application-specific=
 techniques for a whole bunch of problems that were developed in the decade=
s prior.</span></em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size:=
 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>One more time for thos=
e in the back: &#8220;</span><strong>ZK-SNARKs may be to cryptography what =
transformers are to AI.</strong><span>&#8221;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"c=
olor: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><sp=
an>That&#8217;s a big statement. If you&#8217;ve been living under a rock, =
there&#8217;s something of an AI renaissance underfoot. At the heart of all=
 of the insane progress being made is a new architecture: </span><strong>tr=
ansformers</strong><span>. (</span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect=
/e26640d7-ae6f-4624-969a-03dbf4111571?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlN=
